" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mord\">7</span><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span></span></span>\n<p>Le code <code class=\"language-text\">1 101 1011</code> sur un octet utilisant 1 bit de signe, 3 bits pour l'exposant et 4 bits pour\nla mantisse représente donc:</p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>6875</mn><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>75</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">- 1,6875 \\cdot 2^{2}= -6,75</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mord\">7</span><span class=\"mord\">5</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8641079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">7</span><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span></span></span>\n<h2 id=\"la-norme-ieee-754\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#la-norme-ieee-754\" aria-label=\"la norme ieee 754 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>La norme IEEE 754</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>L’IEEE 754 est une norme pour la représentation des nombres à virgule flottante en binaire. Elle\nest la norme la plus employée actuellement pour le calcul des nombres à virgule flottante dans\nle domaine informatique. <a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/IEEE_754\">Source Wikipedia</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Cette norme définit notamment 2 formats pour représenter des nombres à virgule flottante:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>simple précision</em> (32 bits : 1 bit de signe, 8 bits d'exposant (-126 à 127), 23 bits de\nmantisse),</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:IEEE754_simple_precision.png#/media/File:IEEE754_simple_precision.png\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/IEEE754_simple_precision.png\" alt=\"Repr&#xE9;sentation simple pr&#xE9;cision flottants IEEE 754\"></a><br>Par <a href=\"//commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:GMjeanmatt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"User:GMjeanmatt (page does not exist)\">GMjeanmatt</a> &#x2014; <span class=\"int-own-work\" lang=\"fr\">Travail personnel</span>, <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0\" title=\"Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0\">CC BY-SA 3.0</a>, <a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=7318385\">Lien</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>double précision</em> (64 bits : 1 bit de signe, 11 bits d'exposant (-1022 à 1023), 52 bits de\nmantisse).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:IEEE754_double_precision.png#/media/File:IEEE754_double_precision.png\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5b/IEEE754_double_precision.png\" alt=\"IEEE754 double precision.png\"></a><br>Par <a href=\"//commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:GMjeanmatt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"User:GMjeanmatt (page does not exist)\">GMjeanmatt</a> &#x2014; <span class=\"int-own-work\" lang=\"fr\">Travail personnel</span>, <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0\" title=\"Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0\">CC BY-SA 3.0</a>, <a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=7318466\">Lien</a></p>\n<details class=\"appli\" data-titre=\"Réaliser la conversion en base 2 de la valeur approchée de pi: 3.14159265359\"><summary>Réaliser la conversion en base 2 de la valeur approchée de pi: 3.14159265359</summary><ul>\n<li>en simple précision: <a href=\"http://www.binaryconvert.com/result_float.html?decimal=051046049052049053057050054053051053057\">ici</a></li>\n<li>en double précision: <a href=\"http://www.binaryconvert.com/result_double.html?decimal=051046049052049053057050054053051053057\">ici</a></li>\n</ul><p>Comparer la précision obtenue dans les deux cas.</p></details>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-2020/1g/nsi/2-representation-des-donnees-types-et-valeurs-de-base/5-representation-approximative-des-nombres-reels/#notion-de-nombre-flottant\">Notion de nombre flottant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-2020/1g/nsi/2-representation-des-donnees-types-et-valeurs-de-base/5-representation-approximative-des-nombres-reels/#principe-du-codage\">Principe du codage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-2020/1g/nsi/2-representation-des-donnees-types-et-valeurs-de-base/5-representation-approximative-des-nombres-reels/#la-norme-ieee-754\">La norme IEEE 754</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"tags":["base 2","encodage","nombres à virgule","nombres flottants"]},"fields":{"classe":"1g","chapter":"Représentation approximative des nombres réels","matter":"nsi","nChapter":"5","part":"Représentation des données : types et valeurs de base","nPart":"2"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"1g/nsi/2-representation-des-donnees-types-et-valeurs-de-base/5-representation-approximative-des-nombres-reels","chapter":"Représentation approximative des nombres réels"}}}